name: Quipped - A Word Game for Friends!
description: Every day Quipped challenges you and your friends to produce a word with the highest score from today's puzzle! Each morning a unique set of letters is generated – the same for every player in the world. The goal is to create the longest word or words that involve the most unique letters to score the most points. Vowels, for example, are worth a single point while more exotic letters like Q and Z are worth the maximum of 10. You get as many attempts as you want, and can easily share your score with friends and social media. Social sharing is easy and hides the actual letters used by the player, while showing their scores.
